Dear <%= @invite.name %>,

Thank you for your RSVP! Here's a summary of what we have on file:

<% @guests.each do |guest| %>
<%= guest.full_name %>
<% @events.each do |event| %>
<% rsvp = guest.rsvp_for(event) %>
  <%= event.name %>: <%= rsvp&.attending == true ? "Joyfully accepts" : rsvp&.attending == false ? "Regretfully declines" : "Pending" %>
<% end %>
<% if guest.meal_choice != "tbd" %>  Meal: <%= guest.meal_choice.titleize %><% end %>
<% if guest.dietary_notes.present? %>  Dietary notes: <%= guest.dietary_notes %><% end %>
<% if guest.needs_childcare? %>  Needs childcare<% end %>

<% end %>
Need to make changes? You can update your RSVP anytime:
<%= @manage_url %>

<%= WEDDING[:couple_names] %>
example.wedding
